{"tid":1846223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實佢巴士開啲關口B車出嚟 我哋set rb係冇用","createTime":"2020-01-27T13:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T02:24:19.000Z","uid":158977,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f0842efdd02056709d88b6f2b4b2cf8c13825d","tid":1846223,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"車開咗就開咗 除非係喺關口攔截<br />\n因為巴士可以隨時開門放客落地行 set rb冇意思 <br />\n除非邊個落車就召喚神獸 但咁樣都係冇意思 大家坐喺度等<br />\n<br />\n我有幾個大致嘅方向<br />\n1。逼城巴唔出車 得返的士可以選擇 可以減慢問題 但不能根治 而dc狗有客實做<br />\n<br />\n2。令城巴出唔到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你明的（唔建議）<br />\n<br />\n以深圳灣關口為例 喺深圳灣條橋rb 打回頭 但點去 點撤退係一個問題<br />\n<br />\n注意 一入咗深圳灣口岸內係入得唔出得 冇其他路 佔領口岸唔係一個選項<br />\n一有狗rb咗橋 我哋就同藍絲仆街攬住死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他關口 本打手唔熟<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"28060d9657162e031195f8ec7eca2ac4a48dedd0","tid":1846223,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:57:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a48f6e603811a077b020d5b70fe3d417e198f996","tid":1846223,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45192f4d746b7cd2fc6283e65b5981895b0fb54b","tid":1846223,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:01:56.000Z","msg":"得返一日時間 一句講晒  1.29罷工加黎明行動 做定唔做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846030</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6087